title: Umi v0.0.2
description:
Umi is a fast-paced runner set in a post-apocalyptic world in which Umi, a seagull with a struggling family, must overcome the dangers that surround him and save his loved ones from imminent death. 

Brave the elements through hostile lands, collect resources as you go, and cut - or shoot! - your way to the high score!

*Dynamic, infinite gameplay makes each play-through of Umi a unique tactical challenge.

*Umi's hand-drawn environments and charming character design provide a lush, immersive experience.

*Tight touch controls and addictive gun-play will leave you breathless.

NO IN-APP PURCHASES AND NO ADS! JUST PLAY!

*Expect regular updates with free new content!

What's New:

- Leaderboards have been added!
- Yeti has been patched back in!
- Hitboxes have been revamped!
- A Jump/ Attack button swap has been added to the pause menu!
